caption: June 16th is the #Egyptian "Night of the #Teardrop" festival when #Isis weeps for slain #Osiris. #Intersex #Nile #inundation deity #HAPI collects a #tear, spawning the July #flood. #Hadrian wept for #Antinous, who interceded with #Hapy for a #miracle flood: https://antinousstars.blogspot.com/2021/06/we-remember-night-of-teardrop-when.html
